[Abstract] [Keywords]

In the Perspective of 2030 and Beyond, the 6G Network with integrated sensing, communication and computing becomes the foundation for societal digital transformation. Currently, the industry is mainly focused on research related to integrated communication and sensing. Therefore, this paper, from the vantage point of network system architecture design and application deployment, presents a comprehensive design scheme for an integrated sensing, communication, and computing network. The paper introduces key aspects such as system functionality, wireless air interface design, multi-modal collaborative sensing, computational resource provisioning, service orchestration, network scheduling, security, and more. Finally, the paper presents a performance evaluation framework tailored for networks and services oriented towards integrated sensing, communication, and computing. 6G; 6G network architecture; integrated sensing, communication and computing network architecture; integrated sensing and communication; integrated communication and computing

